            "icon_width": 48,
            "subheading": "Our purpose",
            "title": "The power of mealtimes",
            "content": "<p>We believe mealtimes <strong>are more than just eating</strong>. They're an opportunity to educate our children, enjoy shared experiences and build life-long memories. </p><p>But only with the <strong>right tools.</strong></p><p>By combining <strong>deep child development insights with advanced design and engineering </strong>we've created innovative feeding tools that intuitively teach your child to eat, all on their own. Helping to unleash their independence, and <strong>increasing their skills and confidence</strong> every single mealtime.<br/><br/>And at doddl, we think independence really matters, because for a child,<strong> ‘I can do it!</strong>’ is immensly powerful and the confidence it instils creates the foundations for them to blossom and grow into <strong>inspired adults who have the ability to inspire the world.</strong></p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "background": "#ffffff",
