    "timeline_YQy9PF": {
      "type": "timeline",
      "blocks": {
        "slide_NthmYq": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Messy_Eating1.jpg",
            "navigation_label": "2013",
            "subheading": "2013",
            "title": "Idea for designing first technologically advanced cutlery for toddlers.",
            "content": "<p>Born out of stressful and messy mealtimes with her children, doddl Founder Cat longed for a more enjoyable and relaxing experience. While on holiday with her family, her daughter’s fork handle broke, but she proceeded to use the stubby utensil end much more effectively. In that moment Cat envisioned a <a href=\"https://doddl.com/products/doddl-toddler-feeding-set\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://doddl.com/products/doddl-toddler-feeding-set\">toddler cutlery set</a> that was specifically engineered to help young children succeed immediately, whilst developing critical motor skills. </p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_RLwtED": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/kids.jpg",
            "navigation_label": "2015",
            "subheading": "2015",
            "title": "doddl launches with a successful crowdfunding campaign.",
            "content": "<p>Following nearly 2 years of extensive research, testing and numerous design iterations, combined with the critical input from child development experts, the final prototypes are created. Doddl is officially launched to the public through Kickstarter crowd funding. Following this, we are selected as finalists for the Great British Inventors Project</p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_GJByjc": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Retail_launch_2016.jpg",
            "navigation_label": "2017",
            "subheading": "2017",
            "title": "doddl available in major retail (UK) and sells to over 20 countries.",
            "content": "<p>Now available in JoJo Maman Bebe & Boots in the UK and is sold in Australia, France, Poland, Lithuania and more.</p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_KtpdGY": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/japan.png",
            "navigation_label": "2018",
            "subheading": "2018",
            "title": "Multi-award-winning doddl launches successfully in Japan and Taiwan.",
            "content": "<p>Through new partnerships established in Japan and Taiwan doddl launches successfully in to these 2 key markets. doddl is featured on a popular Taiwanese reality TV show. </p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_eYYMxw": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/baby_cutlery_launches_2019.jpg",
            "navigation_label": "2019 & 2020",
            "subheading": "2019 & 2020",
            "title": "doddl baby cutlery launches to market",
            "content": "<p>Following on from the success of doddl toddler cutlery, it was time to design a solution for babies from 6 months. Modelled on the original doddl design but re-engineered for a babies development, doddl baby cutlery was born. </p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_TDAfGi": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/plates.jpg",
            "navigation_label": "2021",
            "subheading": "2021",
            "title": "Celebrity fans share their doddl experience and the doddl plate launches.",
            "content": "<p>Having purchased doddl, Joe Wicks, Gemma Atkinson, Lucy Mecklenburgh, Deliciously Ella, Camilla Thurlow and Kate Lawler share their doddl experiences. The doddl plate, with clever design features becomes the newest product in the doddl range. </p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_bAUNTf": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/DODDL_BUNDLES_20_6222_copy.jpg",
            "navigation_label": "2023",
            "subheading": "2023",
            "title": "Announced as winner of The Kings Award for Innovation and a world's first* the doddl 2-in-1 bowl launches",
            "content": "<p>The King's Award for Enterprise -Innovation recognises a select number of businesses across the UK who have demostrated true innovation and commercial success over the past 5 years. On the back of this accolade, doddl launches a world's first, the doddl 2-in-1 bowl. *patent pending </p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_tDqABe": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Blacnk_stand.jpg",
            "navigation_label": "2024",
            "subheading": "2024",
            "title": "Biggest demand for doddl in history. New product development advances.",
            "content": "<p>Watch this space....!</p>"
          }
        }
