            "image": "shopify://shop_images/At_doddl_we_care_about_the_future_of_our_children.jpg",
            "image_rotation_degrees": 0,
            "subheading": "Sustainability",
            "title": "At doddl we care about the future of our children.",
            "content": "<p>It’s at the heart of what we do. That means we take our responsibility to look after the future of the planet seriously. We are striving to make doddl as genuinely eco-friendly as possible, without impacting the unique benefits that our products offer. For us, this is an evolution that we are firmly committed to. <a href=\"/pages/our-commitment-to-the-future\" title=\"Our commitment to the future\">Find out more</a></p>",
            "button_url": "",
