        "item_VfQHWU": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Child_development.jpg",
            "image_rotation_degrees": -15,
            "subheading": "Inspiring children in readiness for their future",
            "title": "At doddl we believe in nurturing a child’s development.",
            "content": "<p>We support and fund <strong>2benterprising</strong>, an organisation partnering with schools to inspire the next generation of ambitious, healthy, ethical and enterprising citizens. To help young children develop the skills they need to confidently make decisions, communicate effectively and contribute positively to their community. <a href=\"/pages/our-commitment-to-the-future\" title=\"Our commitment to the future\">Find out more</a></p>",
            "button_url": "",
            "button_text": ""
          }
        },
        "item_g9z6rj": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Expert_option_1.jpg",
            "image_rotation_degrees": 0,
            "subheading": "Embedding knowledge and expertise into all of our products",
            "title": "Expert led.",
            "content": "<p>From the very beginning of doddl we have worked in partnership with experts from across Feeding, Child Development, Occupational Therapy & Nutrition. Their insights are embedded into doddl products and their endorsements continue to add credibility and confidence to our range.<a href=\"/pages/what-the-experts-think\" title=\"What the experts think\"> Expert Endorsements </a></p>",
